From: John Crispin <john@phrozen.org>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 09:10:23 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 108/109] mediatek: import kernel 6.12 patches from MediaTek
 SDK

Based on commit 5c8ca54b0d2ed2d577d1047a986c4791053875a4 of the MediaTek SDK.

Adds the vendor patch set for filogic targets (clk, crypto, devapc, dsa,
dts, dual-boot, emimpu, ephy, eth, fitblk, gsw, i2c, lvts, net, pcie,
pcs, phy, pinctrl, pmdomain, ppe, pwm, sfp, spi, tnl, tphy, trng, wdt,
wed, xHCI) along with the matching config-6.12 update.

Signed-off-by: John Crispin <john@phrozen.org>
