+---
+[v1] arm64: dts: mediatek: add mt7981 SPI NOR flash overlay
+
+Add DTS overlay for MT7981 SPI NOR flash storage configuration. This overlay
+is part of the MT7981 DTS overlay architecture enabling runtime device tree
+composition for different storage types. Root filesystem reference is added
+to chosen node. Combining base MT7981 DTS with this overlay enables NOR boot
+configuration.
+
+---
