+---
+[v1] arm64: dts: mt7986a rfb: fix spim nand nor dts setting
+
+Fix SPI NAND/NOR clock setting and move pinctrl nodes from base dts to flash
+specific overlay-dts. Changes SPI NAND clock frequency from 10MHz to 52MHz and
+relocates pinctrl configuration from mt7986a-rfb.dts to respective flash specific
+overlay-dts (spi_nand_pins for NAND, spi_nor_pins for NOR) for proper flash type
+specific pin configuration.
