@@ -0,0 +1,29 @@
+---
+[v1] arm64: dts: mt7986b rfb: fix spim nand dts setting
+
+Fix SPI NAND/NOR clock setting from 10MHz to 52MHz
+
+---
+v1: Move openwrt-master files to openwrt-25.12 branch after OpenWrt official
+    25.12 branch release.
+---
+
+--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7986b-rfb.dts
