+---
+[v1] arm64: dts: mediatek: mt7987a: add Banana Pi BPI-R4-Mini support
+
+Add device-tree support for the Banana Pi BPI-R4-Mini (MT7987A).
+Introduce the base board DTS and DT overlays to select boot/storage media
+(eMMC/NAND/NMBM/SD). GMAC0 is configured to use the AN8811HB PHY.
+---
+v1: Initial device tree support for BPI-R4-Mini with base DTS and storage
+    media overlays (eMMC/NAND/NMBM/SD). GMAC0 uses AN8811HB PHY.
+---
+
+--- /dev/null
++++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7987a-bananapi-bpi-r4-mini.dts
