+---
+[v3] arm64: dts: mediatek: add BananaPi BPI-R4 Pro support
+
+Add device tree support for BananaPi BPI-R4 Pro board based on MediaTek MT7988A
+SoC.
+
+---
+v3: Add all pin nodes scattered across different dts into unified pinctrl dtsi.
+v2: Add mt798x flash DTS clock/driving settings (spi0/spi2 pin driving, clock
+    parent config, mmc0 pin driving).
+v1: Move openwrt-master files to openwrt-25.12 branch after OpenWrt official
+    25.12 branch release.
