+---
+[v1] arm64: dts: mt7988: move phys to sgmiipcs and usxgmiisys node
+
+Move PHY references (xfi_tphy0/1) to their proper parent nodes in sgmiipcs and
+usxgmiisys to better handle the PHYA and PHYD reset flow.
