+---
+[v1] arm64: dts: mt7988: add PDMA interrupts for RSS and HWLRO
+
+Add additional PDMA interrupt lines (189-192) to ethernet controller for MT7988
+to support RSS (Receive Side Scaling) and HWLRO (Hardware Large Receive Offload)
+features for improved network performance.
