+From acf499ab612df8721b84fa22016f2d0020bf9b89 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: Bo-Cun Chen <bc-bocun.chen@mediatek.com>
+Date: Tue, 11 Nov 2025 22:04:46 +0800
+Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: mt7988a: change I2C pinmux for SFP RFB
+
+Without this patch, the kernel cannot access the SFP module through
+the I2C bus on the SFP RFB.
+
+Signed-off-by: Bo-Cun Chen <bc-bocun.chen@mediatek.com>
+---
+ arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a-rfb-eth1-sfp.dtso | 2 +-
+ arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a-rfb-eth2-sfp.dtso | 2 +-
