+---
+[v5] net: ethernet: mtk_eth_soc: refactor forced reset monitor
+
+Refactor forced reset monitoring mechanism for improved error detection and recovery.
+This patch enhances reset condition detection, adds comprehensive state tracking,
+and improves recovery procedures for system stability.
+---
+v5: Refactor ADMA Rx and QDMA Tx hang condition.
+v4: Refactor GMAC TX hang condition for the NETSYS SER monitor.
+v3: Add mtk_stats_update() to the NETSYS SER monitor.
+v2: Correct GDM/GMAC ID and refactor GDM TX hang condition.
+v1: Add WDMA Tx, QDMA Tx, GMAC Tx/Rx, GDM Tx/Rx, and ADMA Rx to NETSYS SER monitor.
+---
+
+From 8536707abe1dce317a761162ed7f036f86a48f18 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: Bo-Cun Chen <bc-bocun.chen@mediatek.com>
+Date: Thu, 9 Apr 2026 11:22:27 +0800
+Subject: [PATCH] net: ethernet: mtk_eth_soc: refactor forced reset monitor
+
+---
+ drivers/net/ethernet/mediatek/mtk_eth_soc.c | 239 ++++++++++++++++----
