+---
+[v2] net: phy: update AN8855 gigabit switch driver to v1.0.11
+
+include the following fixes:
+- Disable the unnecessary EEE settings on SERDES port 5
+- Change the wording from 'extSurge' to 'ext-surge'
+- Enable unknown packets flooding on the CPU port only
+- Disable learning on CPU port
+- Add loop detect configuration
+- Fixed compile error of devm_gpio_free
