--- /dev/null
+++ b/target/linux/mediatek/patches-6.12/999-pcie-02-pcie-mediatek-gen3-Add-PCIe-IRQ-affinity-support.patch
@@ -0,0 +1,489 @@
+From 0c0e3ff8b24d2b355c35eaeee81dcc91b77e9d5a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: Jianguo Zhang <jianguo.zhang@mediatek.com>
